Class FileFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • gerberFileReader.Attribute
      • standardAttributes.StandardAttribute
        • standardAttributes.FileFunction
  • public class FileFunction
extends StandardAttribute
    A class to represent the Gerber Standard Attribute ".FileFunction"

      An enumeration of known hole fabrication methods: FileFunction.HoleFabricationMethod.Drill, FileFunction.HoleFabricationMethod.Rout, FileFunction.HoleFabricationMethod.Mixed, and FileFunction.HoleFabricationMethod.Unknown.
